headline.main: Llorente Brace Helps Swansea to 3-2 Win Over Burnley
headline.print_headline: Llorente Brace Helps Swansea to 3-2 Win Over Burnley

lead_paragraph: Fernando Llorente scored twice including a last-minute winner as Swansea City beat Burnley 3-2 in the Premier League on Saturday.
